{"tid":2139544,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"GTAV 香港版超高質　像真度高 + 6大職業：醫護 記者 警察","createTime":"2020-08-04T10:58:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T13:52:02.000Z","uid":311223,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e4f96fc47146b74c34ed91c378d656bfc5c9f09e","tid":2139544,"uid":311223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T10:58:31.000Z","msg":"GTA 動作遊戲於1997年首度推出，讓玩家在外國化身犯罪分子，執行各項任務。現時最新的遊戲版本為 Grand Theft Auto V ，而有香港玩家為 Grand Theft Auto V 推出了香港化的Mod，命名為 Grand Theft Auto Hong Kong City，現正邀請他人參與遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n遊戲設定角色為回流港人，在香港重新生活。香港玩家在 Grand Theft Auto Hong Kong City 建造了一段「花園街」，令參與者更加投入。參與者在遊戲中可以選擇前往「勞工處」和物流中心找尋工作，或者選擇犯罪，兩者同樣可以獲得收入，並藉角色扮演和與他人互動獲得樂趣。<br />\n<br />\n遊戲共有六種職業供玩家選擇，分別係醫護、警察、記者、的士司機、巴士司機和清潔工，醫護和警察工作需向醫院院長和警務署長申請入職。犯罪分子可隨意持槍搶劫便利店、用解鎖工具偷車和製作毒品到街上販賣，更可用近戰武器刺破警車輪胎，但被捕後將會受刑罰，所以犯法與否是全由參與者自行決定。<br />\n <br />\n有興趣的玩家可到官方網站申請加入。<br />\n<br />\n官方網站鏈結:<br />\n<a href=\"https://hongkongcityrp.wixsite.com/homepage\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhongkongcityrp.wixsite.com%2Fhomepage&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4Yd4E4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=8ab1f7b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hongkongcityrp.wixsite.com/homepage</a><br />\n<br />\n報道鏈結:<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/08/04/gtahksixcareer/life-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F08%2F04%2Fgtahksixcareer%2Flife-tech%2F&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4Yd4E4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=91132105\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/08/04/gtahksixcareer/life-tech/</a><br />\n<br />\n大家一齊討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21960256604c0af218923b730139cfe9c4b68031","tid":2139544,"uid":165881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T11:02:46.000Z","msg":"有冇大媽？"},{"pid":"f178a29a87a2b0e8584d24c270117fc98e7a7b59","tid":2139544,"uid":311223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21960256604c0af218923b730139cfe9c4b68031","tid":2139544,"uid"